{"tid":60000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AV女優嫁70歲富商　怕老公會「爽死」","createTime":"2016-12-30T06:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-13T07:18:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf3f0bc522cf722ea39cd396979eef85159735dc","tid":60000,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160825/640_e6e75ce763a15c4f9d17a6e335f357c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160825%2F640_e6e75ce763a15c4f9d17a6e335f357c9.jpg&h=6b4c7003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161202/420_443a0fe9c4f81b46b2d1cd10e1272441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161202%2F420_443a0fe9c4f81b46b2d1cd10e1272441.jpg&h=0a14eb6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國知名AV女優農奈(Nong Nat)，在2011年嫁給富商涅斯蘭德(Harold Nesland Jr)<br />\n之後，就息影從良。但<span style=\"color: red;\">農奈最近向媒體說，她很怕和老公做愛，<br />\n最害怕老公因此心臟病發而「爽死」。</span><br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日星報》報導，現年31歲的農奈，<br />\n本名是茶茶樂佛(Kejsarin Chaichalermphol)，<br />\n代表作包括《東京獵人》(Tokyo Hunter)和《亞洲心》(Asian Heart)，<br />\n擁有DD奶身材。而她的老公涅斯蘭德今年已經70歲，<br />\n兩人年齡相差39歲，可以說是一段「父女戀」。不過農奈說，<br />\n由於涅斯蘭德的建築事業很忙碌，必須全球跑來跑去，<br />\n在結婚的前兩年，兩人聚少離多，幾乎是一個月才見一次面。<br />\n<br />\n農奈坦承，她一度不想這樣獨守空閨，而且外面還有很多男人追她，<br />\n但涅斯蘭德對她說：「只要你找不到比我更好的人，我哪裡也不會去。」<br />\n現在的農奈已經能夠配合涅斯蘭德的生活，但卻出現一項更令她擔心的事，<br />\n那就是涅斯蘭德的心臟有健康上的問題，必須長期服藥，<br />\n她說：「我很害怕他會不會就這樣離開人世？」<span style=\"color: red;\">農奈擔心，<br />\n和涅斯蘭德如果做愛太嗨，她很害怕老公會因此「爽死」。</span><br />\n<br />\n台灣網友則認為：「結果命案現場只發現胸器。」、<br />\n「活到70歲，人若能夠爽死，這一生也夠圓滿了。」、<br />\n「真的會死，每天都上天堂。」、<span style=\"color: red;\">「死了，財産都妳的，<br />\n再找個有錢的老頭，累積財産，一直下去，變成女富翁。」、</span><br />\n「我報名當白老鼠，看會不會真的爽死。」、<br />\n「很多宅男想爽死都沒辦法。」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161202/420_f8504a2add19b814ee1c2b8ee49c8be9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161202%2F420_f8504a2add19b814ee1c2b8ee49c8be9.jpg&h=11cc65ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"932a257c3a181ff3460535c406e8dc381d655640","tid":60000,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"男優定女優？"},{"pid":"e899dbb31cd6b3c813943d8821a624d81cca153a","tid":60000,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:11:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男優定女優？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有乜所謂？"},{"pid":"cebad56bf1696d96c46f4f3f2bd3d0ec8ec132f6","tid":60000,"uid":50620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"人定妖都好<br />\n<br />\n摩牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a85895e123471d959f3aa795975da61a0cea23","tid":60000,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人定妖都好<br />\n<br />\n摩牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pornhub.com/view_video.php?viewkey=78066499\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pornhub.com%2Fview_video.php%3Fviewkey%3D78066499&d=5gUHD5hnZIOw1Z4EuMo5TEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=aa3a3480\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.pornhub.com/view_video.php?viewkey=78066499</a>"},{"pid":"c8d05aba5cdb562fd21f665dbe11c74818526f52","tid":60000,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:13:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人定妖都好<br />\n<br />\n摩牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=